Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-kivy-phytec layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-kivy-phytec layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-kivy-phytec'

II. Misc
========

This layer contains:
- a fix for sdl2 to make it work with OPENGL ES 
- a change in the weston init to allow the LVSD output by default instead of HDMI
- patches for kivy
- kivyMD bb file (Kivy Material Design) and a patch for it
- Kivy demo service 
